::xowiki::Page new \
	-set name en:reference_kv_textpage.page \
	-title "Textpage Command Reference" \
	-text {
<p><u>Name:</u></p>
<p>textpage - Create a paragraph of text with a title</p>

<p><u>Synopsis:</u></p>
<p><b>textpage</b> <i>identifier</i> key <i>value</i></p>

<p><u>Description:</u></p>
<p>Creates a textpage based on key-value pairs. The provided <i>identifier</i> is used in order to reference the element. The <b>title</b> and <b>body</b> of a textpage are regular text stated inside quotes.</p>

<p>Valid keys are:</p>

<p><b>textpage</b> <i>identifier</i> <b>title</b> string inside quotes<br>
<b>textpage</b> <i>identifier</i> <b>body</b> string inside quotes</p>

<p><u>Example:</u></p>
<code class="example">textpage tutorialTextPage title "An Example" <br>textpage tutorialTextPage body "Some text for an examplary paragraph"</code>
} \
	-description {Textpage}
